In the button's [onClick](https://www.wix.com/code/reference/$w.Button.html#onClick) event handler, reset the button's text using the [`label`](https://www.wix.com/code/reference/$w.Button.html#label) property.

```javascript

$w("myButton").onClick( () => {

  $w("myButton").label = "New Text";

} );

```
